Title: 020: Generation Z Insights, Data Privacy and SQL and Database Design with Ilya Eremenko
Description:
In this episode of the Super Data Science Podcast, I chat with my brother, QUT student Ilya Eremenko. You will hear insights about Generation Z, learn about data privacy and get more knowledge about SQL and database design.


If you enjoyed this episode, check out show notes, resources, and more at www.superdatascience.com/20
